# ============================================================================
# BACKUP NOTES
# ============================================================================
# Home Assistant stores config in: ${CONFIG_ROOT}/homeassistant/
# Important files:
#   - configuration.yaml
#   - automations.yaml
#   - scripts.yaml
#   - secrets.yaml
#   - .storage/ (UI config, integrations)
#
# Built-in backup: Settings > System > Backups
# External backup: Include entire config directory in backup strategy
